featured_reviews.review_id:
The ancient temple of Hanuman Ji in Bhusawal. It also has idols of Lord Rama, Mata Sita, Radhe Krishna, and Shiv Ji there.
They celebrate Hanuman Jayanti, Ram Navami, Janmashtami, and many more festivals there.
This temple is located at a convenient place just within 1 km from Bhusawal Railway station. Must visit to feel peace.
